  character: 5
  blocks:
  - context: 0
    lines:
    - "You weren\u2019t exiled by accident. You were removed by design!"
    - Fortunis thrives when the unproductive disappear!
  - context: 6
    lines:
    - Discipline built this city. Weakness threatens it!
    - Every choice has consequences. I enforce them!
  - context: 7
    lines:
    - So the exile returns victorious...
    - With me gone, this city will collapse!
